## <a id="1-0-0"></a> v1.0.0

**Release Date: MMM DD, 2021**

### Features
New features in this release:
* Create and update MySQL instances to configure CPU, memory, persistent volume storage sizes, TLS, and external access. See [Creating and Deleting an Instance](create-delete-mysql.html) and [Updating an Instance](update-instance.html) for more information.

* Support for backing up the MySQL instances to an S3 compatible storage location. See [Backing Up and Restoring in Tanzu MySQL for Kubernetes](backup-restore.html).

* Support for creating a High Availability cluster configuration with 3 members. See TBD.


### Known Issues

* Upgrades from the Beta program releases to the <%= vars.product_full %> 1.0.0 release are not supported. Download and install the latest version.


